<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好耶！<delay8 />好耶！<delay frames="40" />
這震撼人心的煙火發射聲真不錯啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從一開始就這麼精彩，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />根本超棒的啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />唷！<delay8 />我等很久啦——！！<size value="100" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸嘿嘿，<delay20 />大會才剛開始，<delay8 />
當然要豪邁點炒熱氣氛啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看看這閃光！聽聽這聲響！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不用說也知道這是精心製作的煙火啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />
現在不全力享受就太可惜了啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一起全力衝刺吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，你看見了沒？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />閃光與聲響充斥著整個天空喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然這股魄力就是與眾不同啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和死黨一起看的煙火最棒了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣可以加深彼此間的感情喔。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過要是連代溝也一起加深的話，那可就糟了！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" />雖然煙火很大聲，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過你應該有聽清楚吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />煙火最棒啦——！！<size value="100" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸嘿嘿，<delay20 />只要我用丹田發聲，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />音量可不會輸給煙火喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />好耶——！<delay20 />盡量發射吧——！<size value="100" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay8 />啊～<delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大聲喊叫後喉嚨都啞了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等乾脆一口氣喝乾
<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />氣氛也熱絡起來啦！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這座島上發射的煙火<delay8 />又大又多，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是一擲千金呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">煙火就快要放完了……<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />我打算留在這
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直到看完最後一發煙火喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！？<delay20 />已經這麼晚了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這不就代表煙火快結束了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使如此，我們還是得
全力享受到最後一刻喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拿出幹勁來吧——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會也差不多<delay20 />
快要結束了呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使到了活動尾聲，<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
也要全力炒熱氣氛喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
